item.title: Your First Year As A Software Engineer
item.description: Photo by Jasmin Sessler on Unsplash You made it past the interview and you signed the offer. You’re hired! Now you have a shiny new laptop in front of you and are about to take on the world of software engineering… Ruh-roh! Now what? Software engineering is not like other jobs, this is a whole new world. When I landed my first engineering job, I had spent the previous 10 years in manufacturing.
